cast.overview: When Branch's brother, Floyd, is kidnapped for his musical talents by a pair of nefarious pop-star villains, Branch and Poppy embark on a harrowing and emotional journey to reunite the other brothers and rescue Floyd from a fate even worse than pop-culture obscurity.
cast.title: Trolls Band Together

cast.overview: Video game bad guy Ralph and fellow misfit Vanellope von Schweetz must risk it all by traveling to the World Wide Web in search of a replacement part to save Vanellope's video game, Sugar Rush. In way over their heads, Ralph and Vanellope rely on the citizens of the internet — the netizens — to help navigate their way, including an entrepreneur named Yesss, who is the head algorithm and the heart and soul of trend-making site BuzzzTube.
cast.title: Ralph Breaks the Internet

details.biography: GloZell Lyneette Green, better known as GloZell, is an American stand-up comedian and YouTube personality. GloZell established her YouTube channel in 2008, with video interviews, comedy about her life and song parodies.
details.name: Glozell Green
